{
  "id": "adv_main_01_09_04",
  "title": "星見編2章38話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗はどうにかデザイン事務所へ到着した）\n（俺たちはそのあとを、気づかれないように追いかける）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Chisa somehow managed to arrive at the design studio.)\n(We follow quietly behind her‚ so she won’t notice us.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3066.6666666666665,
          "startTime": 7.366666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 6.633333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.366666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、さっきからずっとスマホを気にしてるけど……\nだ、大丈夫かしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa’s been looking at her phone ever since she got here.\nD-do you think she’ll be okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.966666666666663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そういう沙季だって\nスマホを握って離さないじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about you‚ Saki?\nYour phone hasn’t left your iron grip.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.787800407409664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 17.121133740742962
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これはっ\n……すみません、私、また……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-oh!\nSorry… I did it again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.887800407409664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 21.96616786321007
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "だ、だめですね、私\n全然、うまくいかないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s wrong with me?\nI’m doing this all wrong",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.850525247483024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "どうしても、千紗のことが気になっちゃって……\nあの子に自立して、自信を持ってほしいのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m just so worried about Chisa.\nI just want her to be independent and have confidence in herself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.30675735473632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 34.040090688069625
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "これじゃあ、私の方が……\n自立できてない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But at this rate‚ I’m the one\nthat’s not independent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.27342402140299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 37.90675735473632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "でもさ、それの何がいけないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But what exactly is wrong with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.90675735473632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 41.21297049522399
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　芽衣、ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Mei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.21297049522399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 48.31235824426014
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "逆に芽衣は、我慢し過ぎる方がダメだって思う……\nうん、絶対ダメだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I think holding yourself back too much is the wrong thing to do.\nYeah. It’s definitely wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.31235824426014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 50.77902491092683
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、千紗ちゃんに伝えたいことがあるなら\n我慢しないで伝えちゃいなよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ if there’s something you want to tell Chisa‚\ndon’t hold back. Just tell her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7006495433695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 56.00927431583403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そうしたら……\n作戦の意味がなくなっちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if I do that‚\nour plan will have been in vain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.14260764916737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 60.47594098250072
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "私が千紗を構い過ぎてしまうから……\n千紗も私を頼り過ぎてしまうんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s because I dote on Chisa too much…\nThat’s why Chisa relies on me too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.000183455871806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "だからこうして\n距離を置こうとして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that must’ve been why\nI’m trying to give her some space.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.37594107786813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 69.27594107786815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ケンカしちゃった訳でもないのに距離を置くの？\nそんなことしたら、本当に仲悪くなっちゃうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s not like you guys had a fight. Why give her space?\nIf you do that‚ you two really will be at odds.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.62785563541179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は、他にやり方あると思うんだけどな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I personally think there’s a better way to handle this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.18829936186471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 76.18829936186474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "他に……？\n芽衣、もしかしていい考えがあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A better way?\nMei‚ do you have something in particular in mind?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.11340129375456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 85.21340129375457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "さあ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.21340129375457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ないのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ you don’t…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6878683924675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 88.15374139547342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "他の、やり方……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A better way to handle this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.15374139547347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 90.32040806214017
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 90.82040806214013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\n私、千紗にメッセージ送ってみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}.\nI think I’ll send Chisa a text.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.45374139547356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 97.97750564018898
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、心配したから送るんじゃなくて……\nもっと、違う形で送ってみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But not because I’m worried about her.\nI’ll text her with different intentions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.97750564018898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 100.54773364183963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "……確かに、私はずっと心配ばかりしてて\n千紗に構い過ぎていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s true; I’ve been worried about Chisa all her life.\nAnd I’ve doted on her too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.01440030850627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_04-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、姉として千紗にしてあげられることは\n心配だけじゃないんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there are other things a big sister can do\nbesides just worrying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.01440030850628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 111.55482766094917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
